gn=left|[[Ahmed Ayash]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 73 kg|\u201373 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|S Panhga|CAM|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''W''' 11s1\u201300s1\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|G Boboev|UZB|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 00s1\u201310\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Hussein Al-Jarrah]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 81 kg|\u201381 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|MZ Sarwari|AFG|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 00\u201310\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|}\n\n== Karate ==\n{{main article|Karate at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\nYemen participated in the karate competition at the Games with three men's athletes.<ref>{{cite web |title=Official Result Book Karate |url=http://www.ocagames.com/orb/files/4/89/AG2018_OfficialResultBook_Karate_v1.0.pdf |publisher=[[Olympic Council of Asia]] |date=27 August 2018 |accessdate=28 December 2018}}</ref>\n\n;Men\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!Repechage 1\n!Repechage final\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|-style=\"font-size: 95%\"\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|Ali Al-Madhfari\n|align=left|[[Karate at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's kumite 60 kg|\u201360 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|P Lasasimm|LAO|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 0\u20131\n|colspan=7|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Ahmed Garfan\n|align=left|[[Karate at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's kumite 67 kg|\u201367 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|A Al-Masatfa|JOR|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 0\u20132\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Adnan Shaif\n|align=left|[[Karate at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's kumite 75 kg|\u201375 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|Kim M-i|KOR|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 0\u20135\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|}\n\n== Kurash ==\n{{main article|Kurash at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n;Men\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final\n|-style=font-size:95%\n!Opposition<br>score\n!Opposition<br>score\n!Opposition<br>score\n!Opposition<br>score\n!Opposition<br>score\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left|Abdulelah Mones\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Kurash at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 66 kg|\u201366 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|D Damen|KAZ|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 000\u2212100\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Salem Mohammed\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|H Hadiat|INA|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''W''' 100\u2212000\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|B Khalimov|TJK|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 000\u2212100\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|Hussein Al-Jarrah\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Kurash at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 81 kg|\u201381 kg]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|K Soeda|JPN|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 001\u2212012\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Zeyad Mater]]\n|{{flagIOC2athlete|S Shomurodov|UZB|2018 Asian Games}}<br>'''L''' 001\u2212001\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|}\n\n==Swimming==\n{{main article|Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games}}\n\n;Men\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:90%;text-align:center\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!colspan=\"2\"|Heats\n!colspan=\"2\"|Final\n|-style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Time\n!Rank\n!Time\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left rowspan=4|[[Mokhtar Al-Yamani]]\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 50 metre freestyle|50 m freestyle]]\n|23.80\n|27\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 100 metre freestyle|100 m freestyle]]\n|51.51\n|28\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2018 Asian Games \u2013 Men's 200 metre freestyle|200 m freestyle]]\n|1:51.14\n|13\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-\n|align